Scenario	Recommended Model
High Accuracy needed on tabular data	XGBoost / LightGBM
Data has lots of Categories (Strings)	CatBoost
Grouping customers into N fixed segments	K-Means
Finding clusters of odd shapes/Finding outliers	DBSCAN
Need to see the "Genealogy" or hierarchy	Hierarchical
